Before running the application, you have to:
- copy config/database.yml.example to config/database.yml, and fill in with your database connection parameters
- copy config/initializers/local_config.rb.example to config/initializers/local_config.rb, and enter your SMTP server settings
- if you used GMail or Google Apps email in the file above, uncomment the two lines below "tls support for gmail"
  and install "tlsmail" gem
